Here's what we have for you in this update:
- BIG NEWS! Food tracking has never become easier. Fitness Buddy can now recognize what you're eating with just the tap of a camera button. All you need to do is swipe and confirm. Try this new feature by going into the Calories screen and tapping on the camera. Let us know what you think!
- Access all of your workout and other activity history from the calendar located in Workouts
- You can now reorder custom workouts. Tap the blue pencil icon
- Other bug and performance fixes

Your reviews and feedback are important to us! We read them daily to continually improve our application.

Happy Lifting!
- Fitness Buddy Team

Here's what we have in this update:
- BIG NEWS! BRAND SPANKIN' NEW WORKOUT PLANS! New HD videos, easy to follow instructions, customizable to your goals and needs! Upgrade today to start on our new plan and start seeing results!
But don't worry, you can still access the original workout plans by going into the settings icon and tapping "Go to old plans". For those that are enrolled in a plan currently, feel free to check out the new plans by going into the settings icon and tapping "Go to new plans". Let us know what you think!

Your reviews and feedback are important to us! We read them daily to continually improve our application.

Happy Lifting!
- Fitness Buddy Team
